single\"><ac:layout-cell><h1 style=\"text-align: left;\">정의</h1><ul><li class=\"zheditor-p\">컨텐츠 리스트가 화면 내에 완전히 보여지지 않을 경우 사용되는 인디케이터</li></ul><p style=\"text-align: left;\">분류 타입&nbsp;</p><table class=\"wrapped\"><colgroup><col /><col /><col /></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;\">구분</th><th style=\"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;\">설명</th></tr><tr><th style=\"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;\"><p><strong>token type</strong></p></th><td style=\"text-align: center;vertical-align: top;\"><ac:task-list>\n<ac:task>\n<ac:task-id>4</ac:task-id>\n<ac:task-status>incomplete</ac:task-status>\n<ac:task-body><span>&nbsp;</span></ac:task-body>\n</ac:task>\n</ac:task-list></td><td style=\"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;\"><ul style=\"margin-left: 0.0px;\"><li>CSS 토큰으로 디자인의 틀만 잡아준다.</li></ul></td></tr><tr><th style=\"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;\">visual type</th><td style=\"text-align: center;vertical-align: top;\"><ac:task-list>\n<ac:task>\n<ac:task-id>5</ac:task-id>\n<ac:task-status>complete</ac:task-status>\n<ac:task-body><span>&nbsp;</span></ac:task-body>\n</ac:task>\n</ac:task-list></td><td style=\"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;\"><ul style=\"text-align: left;margin-left: 0.0px;\"><li>느슨한 UI 껍데기</li><li>자유롭게 내부 컨텐츠를 커스텀할 수 있다.</li><li>해당 요소에는 어떠한 기능도 정의되지 않는다.</li><li>특정 class에 대해 사전에 정의된 css 를 가져다 쓰는 형태이다.</li></ul></td></tr><tr><th style=\"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;\">functional type</th><td style=\"text-align: center;vertical-align: top;\"><ac:task-list>\n<ac:task>\n<ac:task-id>6</ac:task-id>\n<ac:task-status>incomplete</ac:task-status>\n<ac:task-body><span style=\"color:var(--ds-text-subtle,#5e6c84);\">&nbsp;</span></ac:task-body>\n</ac:task>\n</ac:task-list></td><td style=\"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;\"><ul style=\"text-align: left;margin-left: 0.0px;\"><li>Typescript + HTML + CSS의 한 묶음으로 디자인 요소 뿐만 아니라 기능 요소를 포함한다.</li><li>확장성이 떨어지지만, 사전에 정의된 기능을 쉽게 사용할 수 있다.</li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table></ac:layout-cell></ac:layout-section><ac:layout-section ac:type=\"single\"><ac:layout-cell><p><br /></p></ac:layout-cell></ac:layout-section><ac:layout-section ac:type=\"single\"><ac:layout-cell><h1 style=\"text-align: left;\">개발 사양</h1><h2 style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 15.0px;letter-spacing: 0.0px;\">타입</strong></h2><ul><li><table class=\"relative-table wrapped\" style=\"width: 34.4728%;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 18.8377%;\" /><col style=\"width: 40.6421%;\" /><col style=\"width: 40.6421%;\" /></colgroup><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;text-align: center;\"><br /></th><th scope=\"col\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;text-align: center;\">세로형</th><th scope=\"col\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;text-align: center;\">가로형</th></tr><tr><td class=\"highlight-grey\" data-highlight-colour=\"grey\" style=\"vertical-align: top;text-align: center;\"><div class=\"content-wrapper\" title=\"\"><p><span>Default</span></p></div></td><td style=\"vertical-align: middle;text-align: center;\"><div class=\"content-wrapper\"><p><ac:image ac:thumbnail=\"true\" ac:width=\"200\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"image-2024-8-9_15-25-41.png\" /></ac:image></p></div></td><td style=\"vertical-align: middle;text-align: center;\"><div class=\"content-wrapper\"><p><ac:image ac:thumbnail=\"true\" ac:width=\"200\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"image-2024-8-9_15-25-52.png\" /></ac:image></p></div></td></tr><tr><td class=\"highlight-grey\" data-highlight-colour=\"grey\" style=\"vertical-align: top;text-align: center;\"><div class=\"content-wrapper\" title=\"\"><p><span>R스틱 아이콘<br />적용 예시</span></p></div></td><td style=\"vertical-align: middle;text-align: center;\"><div class=\"content-wrapper\"><p><ac:image ac:thumbnail=\"true\" ac:width=\"200\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"image-2024-8-9_15-51-47.png\" /></ac:image></p></div></td><td style=\"vertical-align: middle;text-align: center;\"><div class=\"content-wrapper\"><p><ac:image ac:thumbnail=\"true\" ac:width=\"200\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"image-2024-8-9_15-52-8.png\" /></ac:image></p></div></td></tr></tbody></table></li></ul><p><strong>규칙</strong></p><ul class=\"zheditor-ul\"><li class=\"zheditor-li\">공통<ul class=\"zheditor-ul\"><li class=\"zheditor-li\"><p class=\"zheditor-p\">Normal 상태 기본 제공</p></li><li class=\"zheditor-li\"><p class=\"zheditor-p\">위치는 컨텐츠 리스트에 세로형은 우측, 가로형은 아래로 제공</p></li><li class=\"zheditor-li\">스크롤 길이 및 마진값은 디자이너가 자유롭게 설정</li></ul></li><li class=\"zheditor-li\">Console<ul class=\"zheditor-ul\"><li class=\"zheditor-li\"><u>R-Stick 아이콘</u>이 컴포넌트에 포함되어 있지 않아 <span style=\"color: rgb(201,55,44);\">별도 <u>구현 필요</u></span></li><li class=\"zheditor-li\"><p class=\"zheditor-p\">R-Stick 아이콘 위치는 스크롤러 상단 또는 하단에 표시</p></li><li class=\"zheditor-li\"><u>(!) 중복 사용 불가</u>: 리스트의 컨텐츠를 L-Stick 포커싱 할 경우, R-Stick 아이콘을 표시 및 사용하지 않음</li></ul></li></ul><p><strong>액션</strong></p><table class=\"relative-table wrapped\" style=\"width: 53.2827%;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 13.1555%;\" /><col style=\"width: 44.8241%;\" /><col style=\"width: 42.0128%;\" /></colgroup><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\">구분</th><th scope=\"col\">설명</th><th scope=\"col\">화면</th></tr><tr><td class=\"highlight-grey\" data-highlight-colour=\"grey\" rowspan=\"2\"><strong>PC</strong></td><td><p class=\"zheditor-p\"><strong>컨텐츠 영역, 마우스 휠 컨트롤</strong></p><p class=\"zheditor-p\"><br /></p></td><td><div class=\"content-wrapper\"><p><ac:image ac:height=\"250\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"스크롤러.gif\" /></ac:image></p></div></td></tr><tr><td><p class=\"zheditor-p\"><strong>Scroll Bar를 클릭-드래그하여 컨트롤</strong></p></td><td><div class=\"content-wrapper\"><p><ac:image ac:height=\"250\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"스크롤러_2.gif\" /></ac:image></p></div></td></tr><tr><td class=\"highlight-grey\" data-highlight-colour=\"grey\" rowspan=\"2\"><strong>Console</strong></td><td><p class=\"zheditor-p\"><strong>콘텐츠 내 스크롤 적용</strong></p><ul><li class=\"zheditor-p\">단순 스크롤의 경우 R-Stick로 컨트롤</li></ul><p class=\"zheditor-p\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p></td><td><div class=\"content-wrapper\"><p><ac:image ac:height=\"250\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"스크롤러_3.gif\" /></ac:image></p></div></td></tr><tr><td><p class=\"zheditor-p\"><strong>포커싱으로 스크롤 적용</strong></p><ul><li class=\"zheditor-p\"><p class=\"zheditor-p\">컨텐츠 영역이 나뉜 경우 L-Stick 으로 컨텐츠 포커싱을 이동하여 컨트롤 한다.</p></li><li class=\"zheditor-p\"><u>(!) 중복 사용 불가</u></li></ul><p class=\"zheditor-p\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p></td><td><div class=\"content-wrapper\"><p><ac:image ac:height=\"250\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"스크롤러_4.gif\" /></ac:image></p></div></td></tr></tbody></table><h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">Property</h2><table class=\"relative-table wrapped\" style=\"width: 38.4141%;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 18.2504%;\" /><col style=\"width: 18.1326%;\" /><col style=\"width: 18.8391%;\" /><col style=\"width: 44.7675%;\" /></colgroup><thead><tr><th style=\"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;\"><p>명칭</p></th><th style=\"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;\"><p>상태</p></th><th style=\"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;\"><p>기본값</p></th><th style=\"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;\"><p>설명</p></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td style=\"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;\">Interaction</td><td style=\"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;\"><ul><li>Normal</li><li>Hover</li></ul></td><td style=\"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;\"><p>Normal</p></td><td style=\"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;\"><ul><li><p class=\"zheditor-p\">Normal: 스크롤의 현재 위치를 표시</p></li><li><p class=\"zheditor-p\">Hover: 마우스 호버 및&nbsp;<span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.0px;\">스크롤 시 밝은색으로 변경</span></p></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table><p><br /></p><h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">적용 케이스</h2><table class=\"wrapped\"><colgroup><col /><col /><col /><col /></colgroup><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\">피쳐</th><th scope=\"col\">페이지 / 기능</th><th scope=\"col\">이미지</th><th scope=\"col\">설명</th></tr><tr><td>ㅇㅇㅇ</td><td>ㅇㅇㅇ</td><td>ㅇㅇㅇ</td><td>ㅇㅇㅇ</td></tr><tr><td><br /></td><td><br /></td><td><br /></td><td><br /></td></tr><tr><td><br /></td><td><br /></td><td><br /></td><td><br /></td></tr></tbody></table></ac:layout-cell></ac:layout-section><ac:layout-section ac:type=\"single\"><ac:layout-cell><p><br /></p></ac:layout-cell></ac:layout-section><ac:layout-section ac:type=\"single\"><ac:layout-cell><h1>디자인</h1><p><span style=\"color: rgb(29,122,252);\"><em>(컴포넌트가 제작된 피그마 링크를 첨부)</em></span></p></ac:layout-cell></ac:layout-section></ac:layout>","representation":"storage","embeddedContent":[],"_expandable":{"content":"/rest/api/content/134187064"}},"_expandable":{"editor":"","atlas_doc_format":"","view":"","export_view":"","styled_view":"","dynamic":"","editor2":"","anonymous_export_view":""}},"extensions":{"position":364168944},"_expandable":{"container":"/rest/api/space/PUBGOutGame","metadata":"","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/134187064/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/134187064/history","descendants":"/rest/api/content/134187064/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/PUBGOutGame","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/134187064/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=134187064","webui":"/spaces/PUBGOutGame/pages/134187064/Scroller","edituiv2":"/spaces/PUBGOutGame/pages/edit-v2/134187064","context":"/wiki","self":"https://krafton.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/134187064","tinyui":"/x/OIj-Bw","collection":"/rest/api/content","base":"https://krafton.atlassian.net/wiki"}}